\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}=x_{0}+h$
\end_inset

 infinitesimal close to 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

.
 The expression 
\begin_inset Formula $\lim_{h\rightarrow0}\frac{f(x_{0}+h)-f(x_{0})}{h}$
\end_inset

 is called 
\emph on

\begin_inset LatexCommand index
