 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $f'(x)$
\end_inset

 is given by:
\begin_inset Formula \begin{eqnarray*}
f'(x) & = & \sum_{k=1}^{n}g_{k}'(x).\end{eqnarray*}

\end_inset


