\begin_layout Standard
The integral of the function 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)$
\end_inset

 from 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 to 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 is denoted by
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{b}f(x)dx$
\end_inset

.
 
