\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{r}_{1}={\cos\frac{\pi}{4} \choose \sin\frac{\pi}{4}},\,\mathbf{r}_{2}={-\sin\frac{\pi}{4} \choose \cos\frac{\pi}{4}}$
